<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #ff9800; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px; background: #f9f9f9; }
    .message-box { background: white; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; margin: 20px 0; }
    .reschedule-button { background: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
    .reschedule-button:hover { background: #45a049; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 0.9em; }
    .reschedule-link { word-break: break-all; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>We Missed You! ðŸ‘‹</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{customerName}},</p>
      
      <div class="message-box">
        <p>This is {{employeeName}} from BetterLSAT.</p>
        <p>Looks like we missed each other for your consultation today. No worries â€” we're here to help you reschedule!</p>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong>Click below to reschedule your appointment:</strong></p>
        <a href="{{rescheduleLink}}" class="reschedule-button">Reschedule Now</a>
      </div>

      <div style="background: #f0f0f0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;">
          <strong>Or copy this link:</strong><br>
          <span class="reschedule-link">{{rescheduleLink}}</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">We look forward to connecting with you soon!</p>
      
      <p>Best Regards,<br><strong>{{employeeName}}<br>Better LSAT MCAT Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to reach out to us.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

